  <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">

    <div class="mb-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-400 bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20">
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400 radar-pulse-glow"></span>
      The operating layer for EOS companies
